➜大学学生面临的选择；打工或者自己做生意
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=1474	9420
读者jimmy yang 写了一篇关于大学学生选择问题的英文文章（很遗憾，他把选择这个词打错了，犯了我经常犯的错误）。<i>"I always consider that what is distinguishing of the job or business. What need me at present, the job, the business? In my opinion, the business is a dream or target, which is worth in abandoning everything that the salaries, the treatment .the support from guys, even no caring the against for friends, relations, wife, for accomplishing the dream or target. While the job just a tool to involve the society and create a platform for your show. Possibility there are many elements such as the salary , the treatment , the support from public and so on to judge whether I should accept the job or not. If some situation is not suitable for the job-hunter, the job will out of eyes of job-hunter. At other hand the job may is changed frequently, when one employee feels the condition have not suitable to him. While the business perhaps takes up the most time of your life to reach your dream and is not changed, unless the dream ---your business have conquered already. That's so-call the both-choose of aspect. But I think the both-choose of aspect make one barrier condition that some job-hunter may wait for another unsure good opportunity and abandon the existent not bad opportunity. The one is as if the bet. I don't know what is done above is right? I also have done it like above situation. By now, I still have doubted whether I am right or not. Perhaps, the time will tell me the answer. But when do I see answers. Only I hope that's a no bad answer at all."</i>
➜俄罗斯第一例反进化论诉讼案
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=1475	16080
<a href="mailto:a.hf9912+solidot@gmail.com">matrix</a> 写道 <i>"过去也许你认为只有伟大的美利坚民族对于达尔文的理论不以为然，其实在长期接受无神论的<a href="http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20061214/ap_on_re_eu/russia_darwin_lawsuit">俄罗斯在进化论上</a>也有了自己的问题。一名学生Maria Shreiber正在控告圣彼得斯堡市教育委员会，声称在Cervantes高级中学使用的10年级生物教科书对于（东正教？）信徒来说是令人愤怒的，教师应该在达尔文著名进化论上提供另外一个选择，她说“生物教科书涉及到了宗教并否定上帝的存在，它伤害了信徒。”这是俄罗斯的第一例反进化论诉讼案。但是学校的负责人和教师对此都不当回事。不过生物教师在上课之前提过对于人类起源有其他方面的理论。"</i>
➜P2P—从灾星到救星
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=1476	18840
<a href="mailto:a.hf9912+solidot@gmail.com">matrix</a> 写道 <i>"MIT Technology Review讨论了<a href="http://www.technologyreview.com/BizTech/17904/page1/">P2P网络技术的未来</a>，尤其在现在这样一个到处都有视频服务的时代了，P2P的角色也在发生变化。文章断言：之前被认为危害合法生意的P2P技术可能会成为绝大多数视频点播服务的基石。"</i>
卡耐基梅隆大学的教授张辉（<a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~hzhang/">Hui Zhang</a>）指出<i>"
因为P2P技术同时使用了用户网络的上传和下载能力，它显然比传统单一的下载要高效的多。P2P的唯一问题是服务提供商如何进行追踪以及决定允许下载多少。张和来自加利福尼亚伯克利分校的同事正一起开发软件，为服务提供商提供控制的功能。"</i>
